name: BLACK AND WHITE
description: a collage of anacam webcam photos. anacam was a 12 year long performance art piece from 1997-2009 where i lived my life on a webcam 24/7. there is a lot of information on this on the net for further history although i must say that pretty much everything written about me is wrong and is a projection from that person. i was an ink blot test, basically. you see what you want to see.
